sources.title: Western Movie | Where Trails Divide | Tom Keene, Warner Richmond, Eleanor Stewart
sources.description:
Tom Allen comes to Rawhide to open a law office. But he becomes the Sheriff instead and goes after Wilson and his outlaw gang hoping his brother Billy is not one of them.

Director: Robert N. Bradbury
Writer: Robert Emmett Tansey 
Stars: Tom Keene, Warner Richmond, Eleanor Stewart 
Genres: Western
